{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Element.createShadowRoot()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/createShadowRoot","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>使用<code>Element.createShadowRoot</code> 创建的实例 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\">阴影 DOM</a>。创建 shadow DOM 时，它始终附加到现有元素。创建 shadow DOM 之后，它所附加的元素称为<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\">shadow root</a>。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>不推荐使用此方法，而使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element/attachShadow\" title=\"attachShadow()\"><code>attachShadow()</code></a>。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"句法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>shadowroot = </em><em>element</em>.createShadowRoot();\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p>没有参数。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果值","title":"结果值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>返回<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"产品规格","title":"产品规格","isH3":false,"content":"<p>任何规格都不再定义此功能。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"浏览器兼容性","title":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"content":""}}],"toc":[{"text":"句法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"产品规格","id":"产品规格"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"使用Element.createShadowRoot 创建的实例 阴影 DOM。创建 shadow DOM 时，它始终附加到现有元素。创建 shadow DOM 之后，它所附加的元素称为shadow root。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element.createShadowRoot()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.createShadowRoot()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Element.createShadowRoot()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/element/createshadowroot","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/